 public offering at $6.25/share, pre-funded warrants at $6.249/share; expects $100M gross proceeds.","id":"68d4fcf7-3b22-45fb-92f7-7af9df49822e","is_major":false,"source":"GlobeNewswire","source_type":"news","summary":"Protara Therapeutics, Inc. announced the pricing of its underwritten public offering of 13,690,000 shares of common stock at $6.25 per share and pre-funded warrants to purchase 2,325,372 shares at $6.249 per warrant. Additionally, the underwriters have a 30-day option to buy up to 2,402,305 additional shares. The gross proceeds from the offering are expected to be around $100 million. The offering is set to close on December 11, 2024. The funds will be used for the clinical development of TARA-002 and other programs, as well as for working capital and general corporate purposes.","tickers":["TARA"],"time":"04:37:26","timestamp":"2024-12-10T04:37:26Z","url":"https://www.globenewswire.com/news-release/2024/12/10/2994188/0/en/Protara-Announces-Pricing-of-100-Million-Public-Offering.html"},{"beta_headline":null,"category":"investing","date":"2024-12-10","headline":"Governor Bullock of RBA: Demand remains excessively high","id":"ffd7e0f4-b7af-4268-b1f0-9a02eb3d4256","is_major":false,"source":"Tradex","source_type":"news","summary":null,"tickers":["RBA"],"time":"04:37:19","timestamp":"2024-12-10T04:37:19Z","url":null},{"beta_headline":null,"category":"investing","date":"2024-12-10","headline":"RBA Governor Bullock: Would Have Acted Today If Thought We Were Wrong","id":"641627df-99b5-4c3e-b26a-91bbd80a706f","is_major":false,"source":"Tradex","source_type":"news","summary":null,"tickers":["RBA"],"time":"04:37:19","timestamp":"2024-12-10T04:37:19Z","url":null},{"beta_headline":null,"category":"investing","date":"2024-12-10","headline":"RBA Governor Bullock: Economic Data Showing Mixed Signals","id":"abe8a9a6-7c19-48fe-9eeb-05f843fe48ce","is_major":false,"source":"Tradex","source_type":"news","summary":null,"tickers":["RBA"],"time":"04:37:18","timestamp":"2024-